OL,3,C'Oldest' Post Office scandal victim
OL,4,Creceives government compensation
OL,6,FOswall Brown died a year after they
OL,7,Fsold the Post Office and Betty Brown
OL,8,Fhas previously stated she believes his
OL,9,Fdeath was impacted by the stress
OL,10,Fcaused by the Horizon faults.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, she told ITV's Good
OL,13,FMorning Britain that she would receive
OL,14,Fa full compensation package after
OL,15,Freaching a settlement with the
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,F"I think they (the government) might
OL,19,Fbe realising they have to get it
OL,20,Fsorted out," she said.
