OL,3,C'Oldest' Post Office scandal victim
OL,4,Creceives government compensation
OL,6,FMrs Brown described how in her
OL,7,Fhusband's final moments in hospital,
OL,8,Fhis "dying thoughts" were that they
OL,9,Fhad no money left, and he asked every
OL,10,Fday about whether the Post Office had
OL,11,Fbeen in touch.
OL,13,FIt follows lead campaigner Alan Bates
OL,14,Freaching his settlement with the
OL,15,FGovernment yesterday.
OL,17,FThe long-running battle for justice
OL,18,Faccelerated dramatically in 2024 after
OL,19,FITV broadcast the drama Mr Bates Vs
OL,20,FThe Post Office, highlighting the
OL,21,Fscandal.
